[00:00.04]--- Lesson 24  It could be worse 不幸中之万幸
[00:05.04]--- First listen and then answer the question.^听录音，然后回答以下问题。
[00:10.04]--- Had the writer's money been stolen?
[00:14.96]I entered the hotel manager's office and sat down.^我走进饭店经理的办公室，坐了下来。
[00:19.80]I had just lost $50 and I felt very upset.^我刚刚丢了50英镑，感到非常烦恼。
[00:26.00]'I left the money in my room,' I said, 'and it's not there now.'^“我把钱放在房间里，”我说，“可现在没有了。”
[00:32.96]The manager was sympathetic, but he could do nothing.^经理深表同情，但却无能为力。
