[00:43.72]He started to complain about this wicked world but was interrupted by a knock at the door.^他开始抱怨起这个邪恶的世道来，却被一阵敲门声打断了。
[00:52.12]A girl came in and put an envelope on his desk.^一个姑娘走了进来，把一个信封放在了他桌上。
